185
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,279
to keep me as a living toy

186
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:18,039
so I survived.

187
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:21,599
The children who grew up in the Ghost Valley

188
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,399
