the head of the Ten Devils!

219
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:40,559
So you went out

220
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:43,079
to kill Hanged Ghost and get the Glazed Armor.

221
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:45,879
